TEXT.S:
Alice in Wonderland u Amuhuwan a kamu, Aylismunyuxiancing u Sakizaya a kamu.
kakiliman <Aylismunyuxiancing>Amuhuwan a kamu:Alice's Adventures in Wonderland, nu suliten mala Alice in Wonderlandatu Aylis tu nisingpian a musiluyay a kakitidaan, nu Amuhuwan a matenengay tu sulit a nanaman ci chaersi·luteweiqi·daosen i sasulitan a nipisulit tu ngangan luyisi·kaluo tu nasulitan nu wawaay a kungku nu cudad. kina kungkuan tu ci Aylisi a tademaw, namakay puhang mahedik ku pawali aadupan mahida u nu sipian a kitaki, malitemuh tu matinengay musakamu a aadupan. kina nu wawaay a kungku nu cudad 1865 mihcaan tahkal tu, izaw ku tu caayay kalecad a mihcaan u sakaydihan namin nu miadihay a cudad. <Aylismunyuxiancing>u micitekay a cudad kuynian mahida tu, pataayaw tu kungku nu wawa a cudad. mipasumadan tu cudad 174 a sasakamuwan patahkalay kuyni.
nilacul
